pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: publications.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: Philippe Mongeon
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  toc: true
  reference-location: margin
  css:
    - styles.css
  variables: {}
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  editor: visual
  anchor-sections: true
  fig-cap-location: margin
  footnotes-hover: true
  listing:
    contents: publications
    sort: date desc
    type: default
    categories: true
    sort-ui: false
    filter-ui: false
  page-layout: full
  title-block-banner: false
